22:27.804 --> 22:30.557
Let me tell you something, Sammy--

22:30.640 --> 22:31.516
Sandy.

22:31.600 --> 22:32.851
Sandy?

22:33.352 --> 22:35.354
There's nothing Sandy about you.

22:36.313 --> 22:40.150
My Martin has done very well for himself,
despite the fact

22:40.233 --> 22:42.194
that he's had to overcome many handicaps.

22:42.277 --> 22:43.653
Wait a minute. What handicaps?

22:43.737 --> 22:46.448
