to settle down with--

22:49.576 --> 22:50.869
Settle down?

22:50.952 --> 22:52.954
He's an old man with a shitty ticker!

22:53.038 --> 22:54.873
He's down, lady, okay? He's down.

22:54.956 --> 22:56.166
Again, kinda hurtful.

22:56.249 --> 23:00.921
